    "response_summary": "The hotel with ID 5955189 has received a mix of reviews from guests in 2024. Overall, the average score is 7.1 out of 10, based on 84 reviews. The majority of guests (35%) rated their stay as \"Superb\" (9-10.1), while 25% found it \"Good\" (7-9), and 21% considered it \"Okay\" (5-7).  \n\nBreaking it down by traveler type, solo travelers gave an average score of 6.1, with cleanliness rated at 6.3, comfort at 6.4, and facilities at 5.8. Young couples were more satisfied, awarding an average of 8.1, with comfort scoring highest at 8.8\u2014slightly above the usual benchmark.  \n\nLooking at score distribution, 8.24% of guests gave the lowest rating (1 out of 10), while 3.53% rated it 2, and 2.35% gave it a 3. The hotel seems to perform well among couples but could improve in meeting the expectations of solo travelers, particularly in facilities and cleanliness.",
